After the destruction of the great leap forward

00:21:17.250 --> 00:21:22.870
that lead to a massive famine. After the chaos
of the Cultural Revolution. Deng Xiaoping

00:21:22.870 --> 00:21:29.020
was in charge, and he was saying his watch
word was the four modernizations. A lot of

00:21:29.020 --> 00:21:32.370
the outside world thought finally there was
a leader of the Chinese Communist Party that

00:21:32.370 --> 00:21:36.480
we can deal with, that seems pragmatic. So
the question was would China be able to go

00:21:36.480 --> 00:21:42.770
from being a fairly poor country, to being
a developed country? Now though, I think the

00:21:42.770 --> 00:21:48.530
big question outside in the world, but also
to some extent in China is how will China's

00:21:48.530 --> 00:21:53.850
ability to have modernized and to be on the
road toward further modernization affect its

00:21:53.850 --> 00:21:59.030
citizens and the world? It's not will China
go from being a poor country to a less poor

00:21:59.030 --> 00:22:05.830
country which was what I think was expected
then. But as the titles of the competition,

00:22:05.830 --> 00:22:10.580
"When China Rules the World" and books like,
that are saying. Look at what a future will

00:22:10.580 --> 00:22:16.450
