The view of Deng Xiaoping changed, when he

00:22:53.040 --> 00:22:57.830
was a backer of the massacre of 1989, but
from the late 1970s to the late 1980s he was

00:22:57.830 --> 00:23:04.230
quite celebrated. Time magazine made him man
of the year twice, which they rarely do. And

00:23:04.230 --> 00:23:09.110
