00:37:52.360 --> 00:38:00.070
nervousness in America about China's arrival,
China being the new potential power, much

00:38:00.070 --> 00:38:05.790
like there's a nervousness though, there's
an added thing to it now because of China's,

00:38:05.790 --> 00:38:12.510
thinking of China being so radically different.
Whereas when Europeans saw America rise, there

00:38:12.510 --> 00:38:19.170
was a fear but there was also some sense of
cultural similarity. But this picture started

00:38:19.170 --> 00:38:22.810
to take on a new meaning and it actually I
can see through a certain American eyes, the

00:38:22.810 --> 00:38:28.240
size of this giant baby coming towards you
might be a little creepy. At this point in

00:38:28.240 --> 00:38:32.330
my talk, you know I'm an academic and I've
tried to do this in a fairly light accessible

00:38:32.330 --> 00:38:38.400
way, I've brought in the John Denver thing,
