00:44:29.470 --> 00:44:34.140
in a variety of ways. Certainly they rely
on a lot of the boom in Shanghai as largely

00:44:34.140 --> 00:44:38.080
been investment. Sometimes called foreign
investment, but foreign direct-investment,

00:44:38.080 --> 00:44:43.361
but sometimes coming from Hong Kong, which
