00:47:11.610 --> 00:47:18.700
than we are on continued economic growth,
because if there's an economic crisis in China,

00:47:18.700 --> 00:47:21.510
it won't just be like the economic crisis
in the United States where a lot of people

00:47:21.510 --> 00:47:26.820
complain but very few people take to the streets.
