00:47:26.820 --> 00:47:33.530
so I think some of the economic worries are
overblown, but I think the worry about, simply

00:47:33.530 --> 00:47:39.840
the fact that the impossibility of the worlds
being able to take the environmental impact

00:47:39.840 --> 00:47:47.860
of China and then potentially other places,
developing very environmentally, degrading

00:47:47.860 --> 00:47:53.840
lifestyles, which of course were partly inspired
